Lands of Myst POLICY BOOK
=========================
We ask that every player be familiar with the contents of this file.

PLAYER KILLING:
Player killing is allowed. See help on CLAN for more
info.

Also a note. There are assassins available which you can hire to kill
another player. See help on HIRE.


MULTPLAYING:
Multiplaying is allowed.


BUG's and IDEA's:
Reported bugs and good ideas are rewarded by the Gods. Use BUG and IDEA
commands. Using bugs is punishable.




